title: Quintal Bioshop
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, European, Portuguese
description: Biological grocery store and organic vegetarian cafe. The cafe offers sandwiches, soups, juices, and salads. Gluten free and raw food options. Store sells ecological products, homeopathy, naturopathy, and natural cosmetics. Organizes workshops on various topics. Free Wi-Fi.
